Rural Development Minister K.C. Joseph said here on Tuesday that wages under the employment guarantee scheme would be issued only through the National Electronic Fund Management System.The Centre has allocated Rs.365 crore to Kerala for the purpose, a press note quoting him said. The amount will be utilised to clear the arrears, and efforts were made to ensure prompt payment to the beneficiaries. Under the new system, the wages will be electronically credited to the account of beneficiaries.â€” Special Correspondent